Subject: Backcountry Camping
Description: Camping can be something besides a place to park your RV.  Learn about what it takes to go someplace where your phone has no signal. How to eat, how to sleep, how to stay warm and dry.  Where you can go within an easy drive from metro Detroit.  We'll  also discuss some of the reasons why you might want to head into the back country.  Speakers include:Clay Dowling - Track: Life  - Duration: 50 minutes - Audio/video needs: none
